message: To get 100 points, first create a 30-point mundane item and a 30-point magical item. Use the vial tool for solid ingredients, and the filter tool for liquid or gas ingredients. Once you have a 30-point mundane item and a 30-point magical item (both will be liquid), combine them to create a 100-point item.

1. Find a 'solid, mundane' ingredient (e.g., dandelion, mushroom, amber, rose petal, bat wing). Use the 'vial' tool on it. This will create a 'liquid, extracted, mundane' item with 30 value.
2. Find a 'gas, magical' or 'liquid, magical' ingredient (e.g., ghostly vapor, kraken ink, whispering wind, basilisk venom, mandrake root). Use the 'filter' tool on it. This will create a 'liquid, filtered, magical' item with 30 value.
3. Combine the 30-point mundane item with the 30-point magical item. This fusion will result in a 100-point item.
4. Submit your inventory. Good luck!
